,"tid":872528,"uid":163340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"近派成日做野 都無追你個POST 而家留番個名先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c417cf47de8fe6ba097c619882dfe4809d746b","tid":872528,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec48d4bf8ab80357d5ddd9d761c7f1954e12415","tid":872528,"uid":163340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"近派成日做野 都無追你個POST 而家留番個名先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T18:17:38.000Z","msg":"近期我都好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以無寫個股<br />\n寫吓哩啲學術嘢"},{"pid":"fd514e217c0bd868f17869f15bb2df69604210d9","tid":872528,"uid":62935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T19:33:15.000Z","msg":"Buffett:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Naturally the disservice done students and gullible investment professionals who have swallowed EMT has been an extraordinary service to us and other followers of Graham. <br />\n<br />\nIn any sort of a contest &ndash; financial, mental, or physical &ndash; it&rsquo;s an enormous advantage to have opponents who have been taught that it&rsquo;s useless to even try. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">From a selfish point of view, Grahamites should probably endow chairs to ensure the perpetual teaching of EMT.&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}